messages.content: What is the purpose of the ComfyUI-Remover node?
The ComfyUI-Remover node makes parts of the image transparent.
What parts of the image can be removed using the ComfyUI-Remover node?
Currently, the node can remove the background and face from an image.
Where can I find an example of the ComfyUI-Remover node in action?
An example image is provided at the end of the documentation.
What are the limitations of the ComfyUI-Remover node?
The node is still in progress and does not support the removal of other parts of the image.
